# Full‑Stack Application (Java + React)

This repository contains a full‑stack application built with a **Java (Spring Boot)** backend and a **React** frontend.  
The frontend is compiled and copied into the backend’s `src/main/resources/static` directory, allowing Spring Boot to serve the UI directly as a single deployable JAR.

